OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1784040488
OL,3,CUK government bans Iran's IRGC for
OL,4,Cbeing a 'threat to national security'
OL,6,FIran's Islamic Revolutionary Guard
OL,7,FCorps (IRGC) has been designated as a
OL,8,Fthreat to national security, the Prime
OL,9,FMinister announced on Monday.
OL,11,FThe UK government has now said anyone
OL,12,Fwho carries out acts of sabotage on
OL,13,Fbehalf of the IRGC could face life
OL,14,Fimprisonment.
OL,16,FIt follows ITV News' reporting about
OL,17,FPouria Zeraati, a journalist who was
OL,18,Fstabbed outside his Wimbledon home by
OL,19,Fpeople acting "on behalf of the
OL,20,FIranian state."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
