FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1784040488
OL,3,CUK government bans Iran's IRGC for
OL,4,Cbeing a 'threat to national security'
OL,6,FZeraati was ambushed and stabbed three
OL,7,Ftimes in the thigh in what prosecutors
OL,8,Fdescribed as "a planned attack
OL,9,Fpreceded by reconnaissance and which
OL,10,Fwas ordered by a third party acting on
OL,11,Fbehalf of the Iranian state".
OL,13,FZeraati was a high-profile face on
OL,14,FIran International, and a billboard of
OL,15,Fhis face had been seen in the Iranian
OL,16,Fcapital with a "Wanted: Dead or Alive"
OL,17,Fmessage, the court heard.
OL,26,@pD@NOUsD@\O]xD@POUxD@fO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/11
