CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1784040488
OL,3,CUK government bans Iran's IRGC for
OL,4,Cbeing a 'threat to national security'
OL,6,FThe court heard that Iran
OL,7,FInternational is "critical of the
OL,8,FIranian regime" and had been
OL,9,Fdesignated as a terrorist organisation
OL,10,Fby the state.
OL,12,FRomanian nationals Nandito Badea, 21,
OL,13,Fand George Stana, 25, were jailed on
OL,14,FJuly 3, 2026 for wounding with intent
OL,15,Fto cause grievous bodily harm.
OL,17,FStana was sentenced to 12 years, and
OL,18,FBadea was given eight years.
OL,26,@oD@ROUpD@OO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
