PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1784040488
OL,3,CUK government bans Iran's IRGC for
OL,4,Cbeing a 'threat to national security'
OL,6,FIn an exclusive interview with ITV
OL,7,FNews in 2024, Zeraati said he believes
OL,8,Fthe attack was a "warning shot"
OL,9,Fbecause his assailants "had the
OL,10,Fopportunity to kill" him.
OL,12,FSpeaking to ITV News on Monday, he
OL,13,Fsaid the PM's designation of the IRGC
OL,14,Fgoes one step towards making the UK
OL,15,Fsafer for Iranian journalists and the
OL,16,FBritish public.
OL,18,FIran International journalist Pouria
OL,19,FZeraati tells ITV News the attack
OL,20,Fagainst him was an attack against the
OL,21,Fnation
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1784040488
OL,3,CUK government bans Iran's IRGC for
OL,4,Cbeing a 'threat to national security'
OL,6,FZeraati said the decision will act as
OL,7,Fa tool for the government and law
OL,8,Fenforcement to monitor and surveil
OL,9,Fpeople who are linked to the group.
OL,11,F"The threat against us is not only a
OL,12,Fthreat against Iranian nationals
OL,13,Fliving in the UK and abroad, it's a
OL,14,Fthreat against the whole Western
OL,15,Fcivilisation," he added.
OL,17,FZeraati believes Iranian diplomats
OL,18,Fcoming to the UK should undergo
OL,19,Fbackground checks "whether they have
OL,20,Flinks with IRGC or not."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
