OL,3,CUK government bans Iran's IRGC for
OL,4,Cbeing a 'threat to national security'
OL,6,FTwo other groups have also been
OL,7,Fdesignated as a threat in a new draft
OL,8,Flegislation by the government.
OL,10,FThese are the Islamic Movement of
OL,11,FCompanions of the Right, and the Main
OL,12,FIntelligence Directorate of the
OL,13,FGeneral Staff of the Armed Forces of
OL,14,Fthe Russian Federation Volunteer Corps.
OL,16,FIt is in response to the wave of
OL,17,Fantisemitic attacks in the UK,
OL,18,Fincluding a double stabbing and a
OL,19,Fseries of arson incidents.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
