FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1784040488
OL,3,CUK government bans Iran's IRGC for
OL,4,Cbeing a 'threat to national security'
OL,6,FThe Islamic Movement of Companions of
OL,7,Fthe Right, who has suspected links to
OL,8,Fpro-Iranian networks, said they were
OL,9,Fresponsible for torching Jewish
OL,10,Fcommunity ambulances in Golders Green
OL,11,Fin March this year.
OL,13,FThe government has already announced
OL,14,Fthat more than #250 million will be
OL,15,Finvested in increasing policing in
OL,16,FJewish communities.
OL,18,FUnder these new state powers, anyone
OL,19,Fsupporting or assisting these groups
OL,20,Fwill face a maximum sentence of 14
OL,21,Fyears in prison.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31108
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1784040488
OL,3,CUK government bans Iran's IRGC for
OL,4,Cbeing a 'threat to national security'
OL,6,FHowever, ministers will need to seek
OL,7,Fparliamentary permission first.
OL,9,FMembers of the Jewish community,
OL,10,Fincluding Chief Rabbi Sir Ephraim
OL,11,FMirvis, were welcomed to Downing
OL,12,FStreet where they applauded Starmer's
OL,13,Fannouncement.
OL,15,FThe PM said: "The Islamic Movement of
OL,16,FCompanions of the Right have publicly
OL,17,Fclaimed seven attacks at UK locations
OL,18,Flinked to Jewish and Israeli
OL,19,Fcommunities, and sitting behind them
OL,20,Fwere members of Iran's IRGC.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31109
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1784040488
OL,3,CUK government bans Iran's IRGC for
OL,4,Cbeing a 'threat to national security'
OL,6,F"So today, under our new state threat
OL,7,Fpowers, we're designating this
OL,8,Fcriminal group, the Islamic Movement
OL,9,Fof Companions of the Right, and we're
OL,10,Fdesignating the IRGC."
OL,12,FForeign Secretary Yvette Cooper said:
OL,13,F"This government will never stop in
OL,14,Fits commitment to protect the Jewish
OL,15,Fcommunity, and we continue to work
OL,16,Furgently to stamp out vile
OL,17,Fantisemitism from our streets."
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/11
