OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31110
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1784040488
OL,3,CUK government bans Iran's IRGC for
OL,4,Cbeing a 'threat to national security'
OL,6,FShadow Foreign Secretary Dame Priti
OL,7,FPatel welcomed the decision, but said
OL,8,Fit was "long overdue" and that the
OL,9,Fgovernment must "urgently explain how
OL,10,Fthis designation will be enforced."
OL,12,FHowever, Lord Walney, who was an
OL,13,Findependent government adviser on
OL,14,Fpolitical violence and disruption,
OL,15,Fsaid the designation "falls short of
OL,16,Ffull proscription under the Terrorism
OL,17,FAct," and that the PM must "monitor
OL,18,Fcarefully whether these laws are
OL,19,Fadequate to keep our streets safe."
OL,26,@{D@cO]
